  Attention:  Creditor/Beneficiary.
It is my delight to inform you that you have been nominated among
beneficiaries that will be compensated in the Mineral Resources Swap
brokered by the World Trade Organization between the International
Consortium of banks and other finance regulatory agencies. This
includes their clientele top of the chains across the world (Special
emphasis on governments in poor/developing countries and the D-20
countries) who are caught up in this weird web.
The condition for the qualification for this gazette are:
(A). That you had/has been debited or that your fund/credit facilities
had/has been trapped unjustly.
(B). That you had/has Subscribed for services that had/has not been
delivered or reversed back to you.
(c). And or that you have been overcharged by tax department and their agents.
This development came on the heels of the relief of the International
Court of Arbitration, mandating that every beneficiary/creditors
should be paid by the debtors institutions via barter.
The translation of this therefore, is that you shall be paid by barter
with an equal value in crude oil, liquified natural gas, gold,
precious gems and other mineral resources of your preference.
For further details you are encouraged to contact our accreditation
consultant Waltz James on: 
wtoa81569@gmail.com
 or Telephone,
Telegram/whatsapp:
+18039980721, to commence the processing of your allotment and pool
terminal for export/delivery to your destination immediately.
Regards,
Ryan Lightman,
special Consultant to ICA & WTO.
